{"sections":{"image_image_with_text_overlay_xLPNLW":{"type":"image--image-with-text-overlay","disabled":true,"custom_css":[],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC04105.jpg","image_height":"40vw","bg_image_overlay_opacity":55,"parallax":true,"title":"HAVE A QUESTION? OUR TEAM WILL HELP YOU","text":"","colors":"dark","textPosition":"center","textAlignment":"center","heading--text-size":26,"text--text-size":12,"link":"","button_label":"","button-text":"#ffffff","button-background":"#242424"}},"image_image_with_text_eRCxFp":{"type":"image--image-with-text","disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/THE_DISCIPLE_FRONT_LAYERED-LARGE_4.15.24_copy.jpg","text_overlapping_image":false,"section-width":"full","layout":"left","text_alignment":"center","title":"AMERICAN METAL WHISKEY SONIC INFUSION","text":"<p>This limited-edition whiskey is sonically infused with our patent-pending process using the signature sound of the custom motorcycle called The Disciple, hand built by Josh Allison of American Metal Customs. The sounds of this custom build were captured and then used to drive the whiskey in and out of the American oak barrel from the inside to deliver a taste that is truly iconic.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","colors":"light"}},"image_image_with_text_overlay_TzftcF":{"type":"image--image-with-text-overlay","disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Disciple.jpg","image_height":"30vw","bg_image_overlay_opacity":0,"parallax":true,"title":"COMING SOON!","text":"The aromas of caramel-corn and brûléed orange prepares the palate for notes of butterscotch, roasted-corn, torched orange and cloves. Balance is maintained with a velvety mouthfeel as white pepper and spice enter towards the back, culminating the finish with a caramelized sweetness that lingers.  The whiskey is pleasantly balanced throughout and leaves a lingering reminder of the balance and warmth.","colors":"dark","textPosition":"center","textAlignment":"ce